text: Prek Phtoul Commune (Preaek Phtoul; ) is a khum (commune) in Angkor Borei District, Takéo Province, Cambodia. == Administration == As of 2019, the commune has 4 phums (villages) as follows. {| class="wikitable sortable" !No. !Code !Village !Khmer |- !1 |21010501 |Angkor |អង្គរ |- !2 |21010502 |Kampong Pou |កំពង់ពោធិ៍ |- !3 |21010503 |Phnum Bourei |ភ្នំបូរី |- !4 |21010504 |Phnum Ba Tep |ភ្នំបាទេព |} == References == Category:Communes of Takeo Province Category:Angkor Borei District
